                    <p>
                        Yan Hai Bin, a professional painter, was born in a village near Hu Zhou in Zhejiang
                        Province and currently resides in Atlanta, Georgia. Studied At The China Art College
                        in Hangzhou, Zhejiang Province with A Major in Oil Painting. A member of Hangzhou
                        Artists Association.</p>
                        <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    <p>
                        Her paintings attempt to showcase Chinese culture using western painting techniques.
                        Yan, also known in English as Anna Yan, sees the world from a woman’s viewpoint
                        by exhibiting a woman’s life in the different ages throughout history. Highly impressionistic,
                        Ms Yan’s work borrows a riot of colors to express the various moods and thoughts
                        of women in a changing era.</p>
